              "free_text": [
                " Polarimeter consisted of a helium gas",
                " scintillator in coincidence with a pair of NE213",
                " scintillators. gas scintillator was a 5cm long by 5cm",
                " diameter cell at 150 atmospheres.  The liquid",
                " scintillators were located at 123 deg. with respect to",
                " the neutrons.  Alternate runs were taken with the",
                " scintillators exchanged."
              ]
            }
